      "body": "In 6d3916f03206cb123da342da1200259e554bae46 \"rpc, wallet: add option to not load the wallet after migration\"\n\nFor `watchonly_wallet` and `solvables_wallet`, without loading those wallets, we lose the output to the user that those wallets were created. `MigrationResult` should be updated to include the watchonly and solvables wallets names so we can return that info to the user when those wallets are not being loaded.",
